{"id":340197,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/03/global-voices-照片集：南菲律宾赏鸟趣/","date":"2014-03-29T01:31:03Z","modified":"2014-03-29T01:31:03Z","title":"Global Voices | 照片集：南菲律宾赏鸟趣","content":"<p><div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10202685077103845&#038;set=a.10202346358676096.1073741828.1106075444&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img alt=\"Pied Triller. Photo by Arnold Alamon. \" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/pied-800x600.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\"></a></p>\n<p>黑原鹃鵙，摄影：Arnold Alamon</p>\n</div>\n<p>菲律宾七千多个岛屿中住有六百多种鸟类，这在这里将有大把机会欣赏这些飞禽的优雅与美。甚至，因为菲律宾地处亚太候鸟迁徙途径之上，尚有机会一睹上千种候鸟。不幸的是，鸟类们的栖息地，正面临都市侵略式的发展<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pages/Save-Freedom-Island-Movement/261825077172453\">计划</a>以及快速自然环境破坏等<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.interaksyon.com/article/58798/manila-bay-groups-invoke-wetland-treaty-against-freedom-island-reclamation\">威胁</a>。</p>\n<div>近年来，<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.google.com.ph/url?sa=t&#038;rct=j&#038;q=&#038;esrc=s&#038;source=web&#038;cd=1&#038;cad=rja&#038;uact=8&#038;ved=0CCgQFjAA&#038;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBirdwatchPhilippines&#038;ei=A94lU8v5OsKEoQTuioCABA&#038;usg=AFQjCNHwbahf_x8BaQxiIluvKG8_0OT8Fw&#038;sig2=uW1pT9nOuZRbpZdQeGq7Tg&#038;bvm=bv.62922401,d.cGU\">赏鸟</a>俨然已成为菲律宾举国雅俗共赏的休闲活动。除了积极倡议提高保育意识外，爱鸟人士还提倡应设置禁猎区来保护国内的野鸟。</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div>数周前，菲律宾野鸟协会成功地在民答那峨岛的三宝颜市举办了<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://flock.pummkin.net/Flock%20-%20Zamboanga3.html#p=8\">鸟类嘉年华</a>。三宝颜也许以治安败坏闻名（主要是因为去年武装叛军<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.interaksyon.com/article/81811/proof-of-zambo-post-siege-build-back-successful-bird-fest-hosting-and-win-in-regional-athletic-meet\">攻击</a>数个村落且拐走数百个平民的新闻影响），但它同时也是数百种鸟类的<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://news.pia.gov.ph/index.php?article=2651394515473\">家</a>，其中包括候鸟洋燕。</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div>这场盛会的发起者之一maiabird，以文字纪录了一些<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://maiabird.blogspot.com/2014/03/pajaros-de-zamboanga.html\">三宝颜</a>稀有的鸟类：</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>我在导览的时候也看见了我的生涯新种（lifer）*，我的第一只暗色岩鹭。可惜牠没有往空旷的地方飞，反而躲进浓密的红树林里去了。但我还是在牠滑离我的视线前，好好地看上了一阵子。</p>\n<p>在帕森奈卡四小时的赏鸟过程中，我共计看到三只生涯新种。我也在数天前参加赏猫头鹰团的过程中，听见棉兰鹰鸮和埃维氏角鸮的声音。帕森奈卡自然公园是赏鸟的天堂，这个区域和鸟类生态很棒（而且寻鸟踪容易），我真的真的很享受在这里的时光，我们绝对会再回来，下次会花更多的时间来探索森林。此外，我还在此瞧到白耳缝叶莺两次。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>她同时也为能在此见到大白鹭的<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://maiabird.blogspot.com/2014/03/daydreaming-about-zamboanga.html\">巢</a>而兴奋，这在菲律宾并不常见。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>当然我们立刻就移动到靠近大白鹭筑巢的区块，这个鱼塘因此变成一个重要的赏鸟景点。大白鹭出现在此育幼是值得进一步研究的题材。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10152244241863624&#038;set=a.10152244279593624&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img alt=\"Great Egrets in a school fishpond in Zamboanga. Photo by Angela Colmenares-Sabino\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/egrets-800x450.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\"></a></p>\n<p>大白鹭在三宝颜一个学校鱼塘旁的巢，摄影：Angela Colmenares-Sabino</p>\n</div>\n<div>Angela，鸟类嘉年华的代表之一，在脸书上发表了她在三宝颜茵特克流域见到菲律宾大冠鹫的<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?v=10152234690198624&#038;set=vb.730963623&#038;type=2&#038;theater\">影片</a>。</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div>同时，大学教授Arnold Alamon上传了在吉他甘拍摄的鸟类照片，此地也位于民答那峨岛。吉他甘的城镇靠近拉古狄根，这里是新机场的建地。</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div>下列是摘自Arnold脸书上的鸟类照片：</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10202685070783687&#038;set=a.10202346358676096.1073741828.1106075444&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img alt=\"Olived-Backed Sunbird. Photo by Arnold Alamon\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/olived-800x600.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\"></a></p>\n<p>黄腹花蜜鸟；摄影：Arnold Alamon</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10202359822132674&#038;set=a.10202346358676096.1073741828.1106075444&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img alt=\"Robin Magpie. Photo by Arnold Alamon\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/robin-magpie-800x600.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\"></a></p>\n<p>鹊鸲；摄影：Arnold Alamon</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10202359823132699&#038;set=a.10202346358676096.1073741828.1106075444&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img alt=\"Yellow Vented Bulbul. Photo by Arnold Alamon\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/yellow-vented-800x600.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\"></a></p>\n<p>黄臀鹎；摄影：Arnold Alamon</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10202405835962991&#038;set=a.10202346358676096.1073741828.1106075444&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img alt=\"Coppersmith Barbet. Photo by Arnold Alamon\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/coppersmith-800x600.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\"></a></p>\n<p>赤胸拟啄木鸟；摄影：Arnold Alamon</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10202685080463929&#038;set=a.10202346358676096.1073741828.1106075444&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img alt=\"Pied Fantail.  Photo by Arnold Alamon\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/fantail-800x600.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\"></a></p>\n<p>斑扇尾鹟；摄影：Arnold Alamon</p>\n</div>\n<p>* lifer在赏鸟圈中指的是这辈子第一次看到的新鸟种，这里与这里有相关说明。</p>\n<div>校对：Josephine Liu</div>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/mong/\" title=\"文章导读 Mong Palatino\">Mong Palatino</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/ameli/\" title=\"文章导读 Ameli\">Ameli</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\